data.description: NO HOA, over 10,000 sq ft LOT, RV GATE & PARKING! Corner lot on a cul-de-sac at 43rd Ave & Bell Rd (LOCATION!). This home has it ALL! Inviting living area showcasing neutral tile floor & vaulted ceilings. PLUS, large FAMILY room with updated color palette & ceiling fan.  Immaculate eat-in kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances (fridge stays!), white cabinetry, & a peninsula equipped with a breakfast bar. End your long & busy day in the master bedroom, a mirrored closet, & private bathroom w/dual sinks, walk-in shower, & door leading to covered patio. 2 car garage includes a storage area w/cabinets, & most garage has been converted to use as FLEX space; extra private bedrm w/private door (Roommate?), an office or recreation room! Oversized backyard with full-length covered patio.
